title: 1Bdrm/1Ba Marina Bay-Sunset Views, Upgraded Condo!
posting_body: ['Waterfront 1/1 Condo, in gated The Shores community.', 'Beautiful view of Fountain, Pond AND Yacht Harbor views!', 'Incredible Sunsets and a Resort Lifestyle!', 'Available September 1st.', 'Scheduled walk-throughs available in August.', 'Condo Additional info and amenities included in rent:', '-Fully Remodeled- brand new windows installed June 2022!', '-Lower level, has no steps to entry.', '-New modern kitchen, updated bath with tiled showers & floors.', '-Fireplace- recently upgraded with a surround mantle.', '-$2,000 high-end closet system upgrade in bedroom- can easily accommodate clothes for 2 people', '-In-Unit Washer and Dryer.', '-Private patio with pond and marina views', '-Ample private storage closet on patio with tankless water heater', '-1 Designated Carport Parking', '-Ample guest parking', '-2 Pools, 2 Hot Tubs, Gym in the Complex', '-Location has easy access to 580/80, SF/Oakland/Berkeley/Marin, BART Stations, and a FERRY to San Francisco.', 'Rental Terms:', '-1 year lease required', "-First Month's Rent + $2500 Security Deposit", '-$2650/mo', '-Price can be adjusted to include ALL utilities if desired (Water, Trash, PG&E + Comcast hi-speed internet w/ in-home modem-router included)', 'Application Process:', '*Recent credit reports with score', '*Proof of income, references, rental history & employment required']
